msgstr "Pengguna"

msgid "Email Preferences"
msgstr "Preferensi Email"

msgid ""
"Email communication settings. Transactional emails (order confirmations, "
"etc.) are always sent regardless of these settings."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan komunikasi email. Email transaksional (konfirmasi pesanan, dll.) "
"selalu dikirim tanpa memandang pengaturan ini."

msgid "SMS Preferences"
msgstr "Preferensi SMS"

msgid ""
"SMS communication settings. All SMS requires explicit customer opt-in (TCPA "
"compliance)."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan komunikasi SMS. Semua SMS memerlukan persetujuan eksplisit dari "
"pelanggan (kepatuhan TCPA)."

msgid "App-Specific Preferences"
msgstr "Preferensi Khusus Aplikasi"

msgid ""
"JSON field containing preferences for blog, loyalty, referrals, and "
"affiliate communications."
msgstr ""
"Bidang JSON yang berisi preferensi untuk blog, loyalitas, referensi, dan "
"komunikasi afiliasi."

msgid "Consent Tracking (GDPR Compliance)"
msgstr "Pelacakan Persetujuan (Kepatuhan GDPR)"

msgid ""
"Consent metadata required for GDPR Article 7 compliance. Records when, "
"where, and how customer provided consent."
msgstr ""
"Metadata persetujuan yang diperlukan untuk kepatuhan GDPR Pasal 7. Mencatat "
"kapan, di mana, dan bagaimana pelanggan memberikan persetujuan."

msgid "Unsubscribe"
msgstr "Batalkan Langganan"

msgid "Unique token for one-click unsubscribe links in marketing emails."
msgstr ""
"Token unik untuk tautan batalkan langganan satu klik dalam email pemasaran."

msgid "Metadata"
msgstr "Metadata"

msgid "Email enabled"
msgstr "Email aktif"

msgid "Email disabled"
msgstr "Email dinonaktifkan"

